  "detailed_description": "Set in a fantasy atmosphere inspired by Incan mythology, Pong Temple takes the well-known gameplays of Pong and Brick Breaker and mixes them into a procedural dungeon crawler focused on action and reflexes.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nExplore the temple, collect resources to create custom playable rooms and share them on the Workshop, collect artifacts to become stronger, and complete 18 challenges to unlock new artifacts that will help you conquer the temple.",
